sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Istio as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS Proxy
    participant REST as Drogon HTTP Server<br/>REST port/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as gRPC Server<br/>gRPC port/TCP HTTP2
    participant Handler as http_rest_api_handler<br/>API Key Check
    participant KFS as KFS gRPC Service
    participant MM as ModelManager
    participant MP as MediaPipe Graph<br/>Executor
    participant LLMCalc as HttpLLMCalculator
    participant GenAI as GenAI Servable<br/>Continuous Batching
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime<br/>CPU/GPU/NPU
    participant FSFactory as FilesystemFactory
    participant Cloud as Cloud Storage<br/>S3/Azure/GCS<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Cloud: Flow 1: REST Inference Request (TFS v1 / KServe v2)

    Client->>Istio: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>or /v2/models/{name}/infer
    Istio->>REST: Forward (plaintext)<br/>mTLS terminated at sidecar
    REST->>Handler: Route request<br/>API Key validated (if configured)
    Handler->>MM: Get model instance
    MM->>OV: Execute inference<br/>InferRequest
    OV-->>MM: Inference result tensor
    MM-->>Handler: Format response
    Handler-->>REST: JSON response
    REST-->>Istio: HTTP response
    Istio-->>Client: Encrypted response

    Note over Client,Cloud: Flow 2: gRPC Streaming LLM Inference (OpenAI-compatible via gRPC)

    Client->>Istio: ModelStreamInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    Istio->>gRPC: Forward (plaintext)<br/>InsecureServerCredentials
    gRPC->>KFS: Route to KFS service
    KFS->>MP: Execute MediaPipe graph
    MP->>LLMCalc: Process through<br/>HttpLLMCalculator
    LLMCalc->>GenAI: Continuous batching<br/>inference request
    GenAI->>OV: Token generation loop<br/>OpenVINO GenAI Runtime

    loop Streaming tokens
        OV-->>GenAI: Next token
        GenAI-->>LLMCalc: Generated token
        LLMCalc-->>MP: Loopback control signal
        MP-->>KFS: Streaming partial response
        KFS-->>gRPC: gRPC stream chunk
        gRPC-->>Istio: Stream forward
        Istio-->>Client: Encrypted stream chunk
    end

    Note over Client,Cloud: Flow 3: REST Chat Completions (OpenAI-compatible SSE)

    Client->>Istio: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>{"stream": true}
    Istio->>REST: Forward (plaintext)
    REST->>Handler: Route to OpenAI handler
    Handler->>MP: Execute LLM graph
    MP->>LLMCalc: Process chat template<br/>(Jinja2)
    LLMCalc->>GenAI: Tokenize + generate
    GenAI->>OV: Inference loop

    loop SSE Streaming
        OV-->>GenAI: Next token
        GenAI-->>LLMCalc: Token + finish reason
        LLMCalc-->>Handler: SSE event
        Handler-->>REST: data: {"choices":[...]}
        REST-->>Istio: SSE chunk
        Istio-->>Client: Encrypted SSE
    end

    Note over Client,Cloud: Flow 4: Model Loading from Cloud Storage

    MM->>FSFactory: Resolve model path<br/>(s3://, az://, gs://)
    FSFactory->>Cloud: List objects / Download<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / Azure SDK / GCS SA
    Cloud-->>FSFactory: Model artifacts
    FSFactory-->>MM: Local cached model files
    MM->>OV: LoadModel(path)<br/>Compile for target device
    OV-->>MM: Model loaded successfully
